title: 819. Miami Heat's Culture & 5th-Year Options Declined
itunes:title: 819. Miami Heat's Culture & 5th-Year Options Declined
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys discuss how the Miami Heat developed a winning culture and built their team. Then, for the rest of the show, the pair discuss fifth-year options that were declined by teams.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
